subject.value: An administrator created an account for you at Drupal CMS

body_html.value:
joshuami,

A site administrator at Drupal CMS has created an account for you. You may now log in by clicking this link:

Log in and set your password

This link can only be used once to log in and will lead you to a page where you can set your password.

After setting your password, you will be able to log in at https://joshuami2.ddev.site/user in the future using:

username: joshuami
password: Your password

--  Drupal CMS team
